1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:22,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,120
Who's trying to intimidate who here?

3
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:40,039
And who exactly runs this household?

4
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:41,950
I'm all ears.

5
00:01:44,789 --> 00:01:46,150
You misheard me.

6
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,229
What brings you

7
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:50,710
to my quarters at this hour?

8
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,350
Don't you brew medicine

9
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:53,680
for Madam every day?

10
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:55,590
I've come to learn how.

11
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,310
There we go.

12
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:46,430
Master!

13
00:02:46,750 --> 00:02:47,240
She...

14
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,520
She is being completely unreasonable!

15
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,840
Look what she's done to me!

16
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,800
It's just brewing medicine.

17
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,190
No need to make a fuss.

18
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,280
Just brew another batch.

19
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,710
That's not right.

20
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,910
She clearly can't brew medicine,

21
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,870
yet Nanny Zhou lied right to our faces,

22
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:09,360
saying she does it

23
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,710
for Madam every day.

24
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,400
Even when I caught her red-handed,

25
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,520
she still denied it

26
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,080
and forced Concubine Song to brew it.

27
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:15,870
Then,

28
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,470
the medicine spilled,

29
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:19,750
and Concubine Song

30
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:21,280
nearly caught fire herself.

31
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,470
Nanny,

32
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:25,960
you're making trouble for no reason.

33
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,870
Are you that bored of peace?

34
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,150
Deliberately sowing discord

35
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:30,750
between Madam and Lady Song?

36
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:31,680
I...

37
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,150
I'm innocent!

38
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,680
What I meant was,

39
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,590
she supervises the brewing every night,

40
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,630
she doesn't do it herself!

41
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,750
It was just

42
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,240
a slip of the tongue!

43
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:41,590
That's right.

44
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,280
Madam,

45
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,710
you know

46
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,190
what kind of person I am.

47
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:00,280
Jinzhao just came back,

48
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,560
she doesn't know

49
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:04,840
all the ins and outs here.

50
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:10,630
How would I not know?

51
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,150
This isn't my first time here.

52
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:14,190
I came once nine years ago.

53
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,160
Nine years ago?

54
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,070
You came here nine years ago?

55
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,000
You didn't know?

56
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,950
The day after my birthday that year,

57
00:04:27,630 --> 00:04:28,720
I came

58
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,800
to the capital alone,

59
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,920
just to see you and Master.

60
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:34,240
But when I reached the gate,

61
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,430
I saw Master with Concubine Song.

62
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,630
Not only did he refuse to let me in,

63
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,310
he ordered Nanny Zhou to chase me away.

64
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:44,510
Master,

65
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,000
- how could you...
- No, no!

66
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,920
That was all a misunderstanding!

67
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:50,190
I didn't

68
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,870
recognize her at all,

69
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,390
I thought

70
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:55,070
she was some street urchin!

71
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,000
I never told Nanny Zhou

72
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,000
to chase you away!

73
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,160
Tell me,

74
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,310
what did you do that day?

75
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,510
I

76
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,560
didn't do anything!

77
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,560
Didn't do anything?

78
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:10,120
She pushed me, hit me,

79
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,630
even pinched me!

80
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:13,480
I ran far away,

81
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:15,160
and she still chased after me!

82
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,000
I...

83
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,870
Master...

84
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,430
This is outrageous!

85
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:23,360
This is outrageous!

86
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,270
You insolent servant!

87
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:30,360
How dare you overstep your place!

88
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:31,560
Guards!

89
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,750
Take Nanny Zhou out

90
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,000
and give her ten strokes of the cane!

91
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,190
Only ten strokes?

92
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:38,630
My neck was swollen from her pinching!

93
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:39,800
Twenty strokes!

94
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,240
No! Master!

95
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,800
I'm innocent, Master!

96
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,950
Drag her out now!

97
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,310
- I'm innocent!
- Move!

98
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:46,270
Master!

99
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,430
Please!

100
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,430
I'm innocent!

101
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,870
Master!

102
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:51,830
Nanny Zhou!

103
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,600
It's getting late.

104
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,160
Get some rest.

105
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,750
Jinzhao.

106
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,160
You're unwell,

107
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,160
you should head back and rest too.

108
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,920
I heard from Mrs. Liu

109
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,510
that Concubine Song's favor

110
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:03,120
made Nanny Zhou untouchable.

111
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,560
She's never even been scolded,

112
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,750
let alone beaten.

113
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,360
Who would've thought

114
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,040
Master would

115
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:10,830
actually have her flogged this time.

116
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:13,680
He's trying to wash his hands of this.

117
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,360
Beating Nanny Zhou

118
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,870
is his way of shutting me up.

119
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:19,920
He knows full well that

120
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,000
if he wants me

121
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,510
to play along in public,

122
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:25,390
to prove he never abandoned his daughter,

123
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:26,870
he has to let me

124
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:28,360
let out this nine years

125
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,190
of resentment.

126
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,600
But I remember it clear as day.

127
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,920
Nanny Zhou

128
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,480
was nothing but a lapdog.

129
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,630
The one who banned me from the manor

130
00:07:38,310 --> 00:07:39,390
was him, Gu Dezhao.

131
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,920
Jinzhao is truly ruthless.

132
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,159
It's been years,

133
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,240
and she still holds that grudge.

134
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,270
Please,

135
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,750
this is too filthy.

136
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,720
Let Liu Xiang do it.

137
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:00,870
It's okay.

138
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,630
You raised me from birth,

139
00:08:02,870 --> 00:08:04,040
so was she.

140
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,600
You even diapered and cleaned her,

141
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,870
you never found her dirty back then.

142
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:08,270
What's wrong with dressing your wounds?

143
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:09,600
Go ahead.

144
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:14,040
Be gentle then.

145
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,750
I'm already being as gentle as I can.

146
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,430
You know it hurts now?

147
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,920
If it hurts so much, stop lying

148
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,070
and egging my mother on.

149
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:22,630
Save yourself from more trouble.

150
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,310
What's wrong with the way you're talking?

151
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,040
It's the truth.

152
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,040
I only lied

153
00:08:29,270 --> 00:08:31,240
for your mother's own good.

154
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,510
For my mother's good?

155
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,000
When Jinzhao

156
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,120
came to the capital alone that year,

157
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:38,600
a six-year-old child

158
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:40,320
who'd done nothing to you,

159
00:08:40,789 --> 00:08:42,390
you hurt her so badly.

160
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:43,870
Was that for my mother's good too?

161
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:47,600
Be gentler!

162
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:49,320
Are you trying to get revenge for her

163
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:49,870
or something?

164
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,120
Fine, fine.

165
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,510
Lan,

166
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,960
do you think

167
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,480
I was born heartless?

168
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,200
Everything I did,

169
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,790
I did for you.

170
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,510
For me?

171
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:08,870
You've been pampered since childhood.

172
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,120
That's only because

173
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:12,750
Jinzhao didn't live here.

174
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,440
If she comes back,

175
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,750
everything

176
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,670
will change.

177
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,870
Don't you forget,

178
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,600
Jinzhao

179
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,120
is the legitimate daughter,

180
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:26,550
and you're...

181
00:09:27,790 --> 00:09:29,000
I'm a concubine's daughter.

182
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:29,840
Nanny Zhou,

183
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,320
why are you bringing this up?

184
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:34,200
My sweet girl,

185
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,840
don't blame me for speaking plainly.

186
00:09:37,790 --> 00:09:39,870
There are things in this world

187
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:43,030
that you have to fight for proactively.

188
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:45,150
If you wait

189
00:09:45,390 --> 00:09:47,670
until someone comes for you,

190
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,510
it'll be too late.

191
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,200
Jinzhao

192
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,320
is cunning

193
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,440
and ruthless.

194
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,750
We all need to

195
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,790
watch our backs around her from now on.

196
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,030
Nie Fengming!

197
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,720
Lord Chen,

198
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,670
to what do I owe the pleasure?

199
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,720
Why did you do this?

200
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:29,440
Why?

201
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,510
Because I can't stand you

202
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:35,670
self-righteous Confucian purists!

203
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,630
Your land equalization policy,

204
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,240
your new tax laws,

205
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,120
all of it is nonsense!

206
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:46,150
You're just trying to take us down

207
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:47,270
and expand your own power!

208
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,550
I'll never let you get away with it!

209
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,200
You're a mere Cloud Cavalry Captain,

210
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,790
what right do you have to go against

211
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:53,840
so many high ministers?

212
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,320
You're a mantis trying to stop a chariot,

213
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,200
utterly foolish.

214
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:01,600
I know exactly what I'm doing,

215
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:06,080
I don't need you lecturing me.

216
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,390
You should

217
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,320
worry about

218
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,150
yourself right now.

219
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:14,720
After this stunt I pulled,

220
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,960
your new tax laws

221
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:19,510
will never be implemented,

222
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:21,270
will they?

223
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,360
I'm afraid you'll be disappointed.

224
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:36,630
His Majesty has issued an imperial edict,

225
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,550
officially launching

226
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:41,030
the land equalization policy.

227
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:47,440
What did you say?

228
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:53,720
His Majesty has issued an imperial edict,

229
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,550
officially launching

230
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,630
the land equalization policy.

231
00:13:08,910 --> 00:13:09,480
You...

232
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:11,270
What did you say?

233
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,390
Say it again!

234
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:16,670
I said,

235
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:19,750
you'll be disappointed.

236
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:22,870
His Majesty approved land equalization,

237
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,150
with Tongzhou as the first pilot site.

238
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,840
We'll explore paths, assess conditions,

239
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:31,790
and set a precedent for future rollout.

240
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:37,720
Good.

241
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,390
Fine!

242
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:44,080
Chen Yanyun,

243
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,390
you won.

244
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:47,510
But

245
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,150
the merchants in Tongzhou

246
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:51,030
are all backed by us hereditary nobles.

247
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,120
I don't think your pilot program

248
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,390
will go as smoothly as you hope.

249
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:00,750
Well, I have you to thank for that.

250
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:03,750
Thanks to what you did,

251
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,790
not a single minister

252
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:07,390
in the court opposed it.

253
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,630
Everything in Tongzhou

254
00:14:17,870 --> 00:14:18,720
is

255
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,960
proceeding in an orderly

256
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,840
and smooth manner.

257
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:36,910
Well,

258
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:39,270
congratulations.

259
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:42,390
I'll be watching from the afterlife,

260
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,600
to see if our Great Yan

261
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,720
can thrive and prosper under your watch,

262
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,960
Chen Yanyun.

263
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,240
Jiuheng,

264
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,270
your new tax policy

265
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:19,870
is absolutely brilliant.

266
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:21,320
Let me

267
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:22,910
join you in this.

268
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,960
You're a Cloud Cavalry Captain,

269
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,550
why meddle in this mess?

270
00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:28,000
So what?

271
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,720
Our ancestors fought and founded

272
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,600
this empire.

273
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,200
I want this dynasty to thrive

274
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,550
more than any of you scholars.

275
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:35,390
If every minister in the court

276
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:37,000
thought like you,

277
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,080
the state of the dynasty

278
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,200
wouldn't have fallen this far.

279
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,510
What if

280
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:42,080
I take the lead in speaking up

281
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:43,200
for the new tax policy?

282
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,240
Would that help?

283
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,960
If you were a prince or a duke,

284
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:49,550
that might do some good.

285
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:50,440
What,

286
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:52,120
you think my title is too low?

287
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,440
I can round up others to join me!

288
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:56,000
A whole list of nobles,

289
00:15:56,390 --> 00:15:57,510
from dukes down to barons.

290
00:16:05,630 --> 00:16:06,270
Enough.

291
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:07,720
You don't have to do a thing.

292
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,240
This path is far too dangerous.

293
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:11,120
I have nothing to lose,

294
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:14,320
but you have a wife and daughter.

295
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:17,870
The safety of the realm

296
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,910
is the responsibility of every man.

297
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,360
If this new tax policy

298
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:22,440
can help our Great Yan dynasty recover,

299
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,480
I'd gladly

300
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:26,670
lay down my life for it.

301
00:16:42,030 --> 00:16:43,440
By His Majesty's verbal edict:

302
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:45,750
Nie Fengming has committed high treason,

303
00:16:45,910 --> 00:16:47,150
uttered reckless slander,

304
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,670
and insulted the Late Emperor.

305
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:51,390
He is sentenced to death by caning,

306
00:16:51,790 --> 00:16:53,630
to be executed this very day.

307
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,310
That reckless stunt

308
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:27,880
by Nie Fengming

309
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,070
completely derailed

310
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:30,480
Prince Glorian's

311
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,640
entire scheme.

312
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,590
It's clear the momentum

313
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,550
is now on

314
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:37,310
Master Xuan's side.

315
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:38,720
This momentum

316
00:17:39,110 --> 00:17:41,550
was bought with Nie Fengming's life.

317
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,880
We must not waste his sacrifice.

318
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,270
Once land equalization succeeds,

319
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:49,920
we will honor his memory at his grave.

320
00:17:53,550 --> 00:17:54,270
Jiuheng?

321
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,270
You look pale.

322
00:17:58,350 --> 00:17:59,270
If you're unwell,

323
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:00,590
go back and rest.

324
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:02,830
No one's worked harder than you lately.

325
00:18:03,070 --> 00:18:03,590
Mentor,

326
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:06,240
I feel no hardship.

327
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,750
I believe

328
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:08,680
we must not

329
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,550
grow complacent

330
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,160
now that we've made an opening.

331
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:14,160
Instead, we should seize

332
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:15,830
His Majesty's full backing to plan

333
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,790
and act early,

334
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,510
clearing the way

335
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:20,960
for all that follows.

336
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:22,400
That is the best course of action.

337
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:24,960
Speak. What's on your mind?

338
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:25,720
Yes.

339
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:27,480
With the

340
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:29,640
military nobles backed down,

341
00:18:30,070 --> 00:18:31,640
the biggest obstacle to our new policy

342
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:32,830
is Grand Secretary Fan.

343
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:34,310
We cannot

344
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:36,000
shake his foundation yet,

345
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,310
but we can first chop off

346
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,790
one of his arms

347
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:39,750
to weaken his influence.

348
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:46,830
Who?

349
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,590
Junior Vice Minister of Revenue,

350
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:50,310
Lin Xianzhong,

351
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,310
Lin Xianzhong.

352
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:25,680
Congratulations, Lord Lin.

353
00:19:27,270 --> 00:19:27,750
This way.

354
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:29,720
Please.

355
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,960
Congratulations.

356
00:19:34,550 --> 00:19:35,590
Let me make this clear first,

357
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:38,000
all gifts must be taken back.

358
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,160
The review is underway.

359
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:41,160
Let's not land each other in hot water.

360
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:42,720
We know your rules.

361
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:43,480
We all

362
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,880
came empty-handed today.

363
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,640
Good, please.

364
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:52,750
Zonghai.

365
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,350
Lord Lin.

366
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,480
You made it.

367
00:19:57,590 --> 00:19:58,160
Uncle,

368
00:19:58,790 --> 00:19:59,440
why did you drag me

369
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:00,240
to this birthday banquet?

370
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,830
- Greetings, Young Lord.
- It's dead boring.

371
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,830
The land equalization in Tongzhou

372
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:25,640
has sparked massive outrage.

373
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,440
Several people have already died.

374
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:29,550
The leader, Mrs. Ji, has had her house

375
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:31,590
set on fire multiple times.

376
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:33,110
Now she tests

377
00:20:33,350 --> 00:20:34,440
every meal

378
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:36,110
with a silver needle before eating.

379
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,310
No one knows

380
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,880
if she'll survive another day.

381
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,160
Keep your voice down.

382
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:42,200
Miss,

383
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,270
the Old Madam

384
00:20:44,270 --> 00:20:45,440
is in grave danger.

385
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:49,640
I knew the land equalization was risky,

386
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:51,270
but I thought

387
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:52,270
Mr. Chen

388
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:52,790
would protect our family

389
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:54,000
no matter what.

390
00:20:54,830 --> 00:20:55,480
I never imagined

391
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:57,110
it would come to this.

392
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,720
Lord Chen, this way please.

393
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:02,550
Very well.

394
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,480
Mr. Chen?

395
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:05,750
Miss,

396
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,640
why is he here?

397
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:14,400
Listen,

398
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:15,750
go keep watch up front.

399
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:16,920
If anyone asks,

400
00:21:17,070 --> 00:21:18,070
say I've gone to powder my nose.

401
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:22,350
Are you going to find him?

402
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:25,310
We finally crossed paths today.

403
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:26,440
I can't let this chance slip.

404
00:21:27,110 --> 00:21:28,160
Even if it's just for Grandmother,

405
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,550
I have to beg him.

406
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,000
I'm going.

407
00:21:36,070 --> 00:21:37,640
[Where on earth is she going?]

408
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:40,000
I had no idea

409
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,550
I'd intrude on your wife's birthday.

410
00:21:41,790 --> 00:21:43,880
My apologies for the intrusion.

411
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:46,440
I think

412
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:49,680
you didn't intrude by accident.

413
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,160
You picked today

414
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,640
on purpose.

415
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,750
Let's cut to the chase.

416
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:57,680
Speak your

417
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,160
mind plainly.

418
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:01,440
Very well.

419
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,110
To be frank,

420
00:22:03,510 --> 00:22:04,790
I've come today

421
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,310
to ask

422
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:07,550
a great favor of you.

423
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,070
What favor?

424
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,790
I'm asking you

425
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:15,160
to step down voluntarily,

426
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:17,270
and yield your post

427
00:22:17,790 --> 00:22:18,750
as Junior Vice Minister of Revenue.

428
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:22,110
What did you say?

429
00:22:24,110 --> 00:22:25,550
Don't get agitated just yet.

430
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:27,350
The Criminal Investigation Bureau

431
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:28,640
arrested a man from Zhejiang

432
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:30,400
named Su Yuanhang.

433
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:31,880
He confessed that

434
00:22:32,070 --> 00:22:33,350
he acquired over 30,000 mu

435
00:22:34,270 --> 00:22:35,830
of prime paddy fields in Yuyao

436
00:22:35,830 --> 00:22:37,920
on your orders,

437
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:38,880
for less than

438
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:40,960
two thousand taels of silver.

439
00:22:52,070 --> 00:22:52,640
Oh,

440
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:54,640
and he also said

441
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,720
you sent men to Datong

442
00:22:57,270 --> 00:22:59,590
to dig up dirt on Grand Secretary Fan's

443
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:00,790
family back home.

444
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:02,750
I couldn't believe it

445
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:04,030
at first.

446
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:05,440
Everyone in court knows

447
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,110
how close you are

448
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:07,550
to Grand Secretary Fan.

449
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:10,070
Why would you

450
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:12,480
spy on him behind his back?

451
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:13,270
He...

452
00:23:13,550 --> 00:23:15,110
he's lying.

453
00:23:22,750 --> 00:23:24,640
You're lying.

454
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:25,920
I've never

455
00:23:27,110 --> 00:23:28,830
met this man in my life.

456
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,310
I see.

457
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,400
My lord,

458
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:39,070
the Lady is asking where you've gone.

459
00:23:39,070 --> 00:23:40,030
The feast is about to begin.

460
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,070
You may

461
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:43,510
go to the banquet first.

462
00:23:44,270 --> 00:23:46,000
We can talk more later.

463
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,200
Send someone

464
00:24:05,550 --> 00:24:06,440
to check if Su Yuanhang

465
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:07,440
has really been arrested.

466
00:24:07,550 --> 00:24:07,960
Understood.

467
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:08,480
Wait.

468
00:24:10,480 --> 00:24:12,270
Go yourself.

469
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,720
Be careful on the way.

470
00:24:25,110 --> 00:24:26,960
[I never thought Chen Yanyun]

471
00:24:27,270 --> 00:24:28,720
[could be so ruthless and underhanded.]

472
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:33,350
Miss Gu,

473
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:35,030
Mr. Chen has asked for you.

474
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,070
Me?

475
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:37,960
Yes.

476
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:56,830
Speak.

477
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,880
Why have you been following me?

478
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:01,750
I saw you were coming to the Lin Manor,

479
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,160
so I followed.

480
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:06,590
Is

481
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:08,510
everything alright with you?

482
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:11,000
The Ji family works for me.

483
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:14,480
Don't beat around the bush with me.

484
00:25:17,510 --> 00:25:19,000
You saw right through me.

485
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,880
I heard there's been trouble

486
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:24,200
with the land equalization.

487
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:26,350
I came to ask

488
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,720
how my grandmother is doing.

489
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:31,550
There have been a few setbacks,

490
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,510
but nothing we didn't expect.

491
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,070
Your grandmother

492
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:36,200
has a dedicated guard detail.

493
00:25:36,550 --> 00:25:37,480
You don't need to worry.

494
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,480
That's a relief.

495
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:43,270
Well,

496
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:45,030
Sir,

497
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:47,550
I also wanted to ask...

498
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:48,720
how much longer

499
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:50,510
will the land equalization take?

500
00:25:51,110 --> 00:25:52,240
Grandmother is old.

501
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:53,510
I fear she can't keep this up.

502
00:25:54,030 --> 00:25:56,270
These are not questions for you to ask.

503
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:58,720
Land equalization is state policy,

504
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,830
not child's play.

505
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:05,920
I know my place.

506
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:07,920
I won't speak of it again.

507
00:26:12,310 --> 00:26:13,030
In that case,

508
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:15,070
I'd rather return to Tongzhou,

509
00:26:15,270 --> 00:26:16,510
to stay by Grandmother's side.

510
00:26:16,790 --> 00:26:17,960
It would put my mind at ease.

511
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:19,960
You want to go back?

512
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:20,830
Yes.

513
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:24,720
What are you afraid of?

514
00:26:28,310 --> 00:26:29,270
I beg your forgiveness.

515
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:36,070
Your grandmother volunteered

516
00:26:36,270 --> 00:26:37,310
to lead the land equalization.

517
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,550
Words are not enough.

518
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:41,750
She must take the risks

519
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:43,240
and make

520
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:44,790
the sacrifices.

521
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,440
For me,

522
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:47,880
the Tongzhou pilot

523
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:49,270
is more than just a trial.

524
00:26:49,830 --> 00:26:51,030
It is the first step

525
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:53,000
of the new tax policy.

526
00:26:54,070 --> 00:26:54,720
It

527
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:55,720
will succeed.

528
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:57,640
It

529
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,480
must succeed.

530
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:03,030
I entrusted this critical mission

531
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:04,350
to your grandmother.

532
00:27:05,510 --> 00:27:07,030
She must show her resolve,

533
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,160
prove she is willing

534
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,750
to burn her boats.

535
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:11,200
Only then

536
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:14,160
can I fully trust her.

537
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:15,920
Do you

538
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,110
agree?

539
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:22,750
Yes.

540
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:25,160
I understand.

541
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:28,960
I am that resolve.

542
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:32,750
Your grandmother often says,

543
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,030
trim your sails to the wind,

544
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,400
cut your coat to fit your cloth.

545
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:38,270
No one knows better

546
00:27:38,270 --> 00:27:39,400
than her

547
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:42,960
which way the wind is blowing.

548
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:55,790
Yes,

549
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,550
land equalization is dangerous.

550
00:27:59,350 --> 00:28:00,640
Gravely dangerous.

551
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:01,960
But you must understand,

552
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,880
since time immemorial,

553
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:06,200
land equalization has never been

554
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:08,440
achieved without bloodshed.

555
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:11,070
The blood of our opponents,

556
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:13,510
and the blood of our own.

557
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:15,960
But Chen Yanyun

558
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,680
will never be the first to bleed.

559
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:26,350
Greetings, Young Lord.

560
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,720
Greetings.

561
00:28:29,590 --> 00:28:31,310
Quite the imposing authority you have.

562
00:28:31,590 --> 00:28:33,030
Everyone is paying birthday respects,

563
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:34,000
yet here you are,

564
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:36,310
hiding away in the backyard.

565
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:38,750
I do not care for crowds.

566
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:40,830
You don't even

567
00:28:41,110 --> 00:28:42,790
believe that yourself, do you?

568
00:28:46,070 --> 00:28:47,680
Did you come here to see him?

569
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:49,240
Don't you know

570
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:50,310
a weasel doesn't sneak into the henhouse

571
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:51,310
for nothing?

572
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,680
You jest, my lord.

573
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:56,830
I never jest

574
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:58,400
with men like you.

575
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:00,750
Everyone in court knows Lin Xianzhong

576
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:03,000
is Fan Chuan's right-hand man,

577
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,070
and you are Fu Hailian's star pupil.

578
00:29:04,830 --> 00:29:05,920
Fan Chuan and Fu Hailian

579
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:07,400
are sworn enemies.

580
00:29:08,030 --> 00:29:09,510
Yet here you are,

581
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:11,030
not joining the feast,

582
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:13,270
but lingering deep in the backyard.

583
00:29:14,030 --> 00:29:14,750
If this isn't

584
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:16,590
a weasel in the henhouse,

585
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:17,790
what is it?

586
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:28,880
Young Lord,

587
00:29:29,790 --> 00:29:30,510
Mr. Chen,

588
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:33,440
you two carry on.

589
00:29:34,790 --> 00:29:36,160
I've been out too long.

590
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,350
I should head back.

591
00:29:43,270 --> 00:29:44,030
I'm leaving too.

592
00:29:55,070 --> 00:29:55,550
My lord,

593
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:56,270
Young Lord Ye

594
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:57,590
came specifically looking for Miss Gu.

595
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:00,270
It seems

596
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:02,070
the two of them have grown quite close.

597
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,110
Gu Jinzhao.

598
00:30:10,030 --> 00:30:11,000
What do you want?

599
00:30:12,590 --> 00:30:13,720
Why did you go looking for him?

600
00:30:15,070 --> 00:30:16,030
It's none of your business.

601
00:30:17,830 --> 00:30:18,720
I'm warning you.

602
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,480
You'd better stay away from him.

603
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,030
What do you mean?

604
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:25,160
I know you hate your father,

605
00:30:25,510 --> 00:30:26,750
but you still bear the Gu family name.

606
00:30:27,110 --> 00:30:28,160
Do you know the entire Gu family

607
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,400
is in Fan Chuan's faction?

608
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:31,550
I didn't before.

609
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:32,640
I do now.

610
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,110
That's why I need to get back quickly.

611
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:36,400
You...

612
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:40,590
Cheers.

613
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:41,720
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

614
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:42,510
- Drink.
- Cheers.

615
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:46,550
Master,

616
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:49,310
the young lady wishes to leave early.

617
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,310
Help yourselves, everyone.

618
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:57,880
The feast is barely halfway through.

619
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,200
How can you want to leave?

620
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:01,030
Where's your manner?

621
00:31:04,030 --> 00:31:04,830
Stand aside.

622
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:09,160
Master,

623
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,680
Madam has sudden heart palpitations.

624
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:11,830
Madam is calling for you to return.

625
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:16,000
How could this happen?

626
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:19,070
Lord Lin,

627
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:20,920
my wife has fallen suddenly ill.

628
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:22,830
I cannot stay,

629
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,070
I must take my leave.

630
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:26,110
Of course.

631
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:27,880
Your wife's health comes first.

632
00:31:28,070 --> 00:31:29,000
Go.

633
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:29,590
Very well.

634
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:31,310
How did she suddenly have heart pains?

635
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:32,440
Should I

636
00:31:32,750 --> 00:31:33,790
- come with you?
- Dezhao,

637
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:34,720
you stay here.

638
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:37,000
I'll take him back first

639
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:37,920
to check on her.

640
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:38,640
Let's go.

641
00:31:39,720 --> 00:31:41,480
You hurry back to see her.

642
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:45,000
Miss Gu.

643
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:49,270
Miss Gu,

644
00:31:49,270 --> 00:31:50,200
- you look
- Mentor,

645
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,400
- absolutely stunning today.
- to be frank,

646
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,400
if my

647
00:31:52,750 --> 00:31:54,000
mother-in-law hadn't stopped me,

648
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:56,400
I would have brought

649
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:57,720
the child back long ago.

650
00:31:58,400 --> 00:31:59,750
I don't mind you all laughing.

651
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:01,160
I'm just a man

652
00:32:01,790 --> 00:32:02,550
who cares

653
00:32:03,270 --> 00:32:05,000
deeply for his children.

654
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:07,640
Miss Gu,

655
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:09,510
- your father is so good to you.
- Eat.

656
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,640
[How dare he say that.]

657
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:13,550
[No,]

658
00:32:13,750 --> 00:32:14,790
[I have to think of something.]

659
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,240
Yes,

660
00:32:16,720 --> 00:32:17,510
though I live

661
00:32:17,830 --> 00:32:19,590
in Tongzhou most days,

662
00:32:20,110 --> 00:32:21,110
my father

663
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,920
comes to visit me often.

664
00:32:23,590 --> 00:32:24,880
He and his concubine

665
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:26,200
even made the trip specially

666
00:32:26,590 --> 00:32:28,110
for my coming-of-age ceremony

667
00:32:28,350 --> 00:32:29,750
in Tongzhou.

668
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:35,000
My wife is in poor health

669
00:32:35,550 --> 00:32:36,640
and cannot stand traveling.

670
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,590
The household affairs have long been

671
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:39,960
managed by one of my concubines,

672
00:32:40,110 --> 00:32:40,920
so I

673
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:42,070
brought her along

674
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:43,480
to the ceremony in Tongzhou.

675
00:32:44,550 --> 00:32:45,590
Indeed.

676
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,960
My concubine is from a prestigious clan,

677
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:49,480
well-educated and refined.

678
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:51,270
She is the daughter of the former

679
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:52,880
Chief of the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

680
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:54,790
Really?

681
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,510
Could it be Song Shiqi,

682
00:32:56,510 --> 00:32:58,200
who retired from office

683
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,200
five years ago?

684
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,590
To think he would

685
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,400
marry his daughter

686
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:05,590
to Lord Gu as a concubine.

687
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:07,030
Truly remarkable.

688
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:07,960
One dared to marry into it,

689
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:09,400
the other dared to take her.

690
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:13,550
You never

691
