694
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:22,110
so my mother arranged for me

695
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:24,590
to take Lady Song as a concubine.

696
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:27,590
I knew it was improper,

697
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:28,440
so

698
