has no right to run the household.

701
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:38,790
You are quite right.

702
00:33:39,270 --> 00:33:40,720
My mother also said,

703
00:33:41,030 --> 00:33:42,110
if my wife's health

704
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:43,880
does not improve,

705
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:44,720
we should move back

706
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:45,960
to the family's ancestral estate,

707
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:47,790
