but I never believed it until now.

717
00:34:06,510 --> 00:34:08,630
It's truly opened my eyes.

718
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:09,960
For example,

719
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:11,550
Lady Song drinks a bowl of

720
00:34:11,710 --> 00:34:12,280
