725
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:20,920
Shut your mouth.

726
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,000
I...

727
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:29,440
I must take my leave.

728
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,030
Let's go.

729
00:34:43,630 --> 00:34:44,230
Sir,

730
00:34:44,510 --> 00:34:45,360
just as you expected.

731
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:46,590
Lin Xianzhong did send someone

732
00:34:46,590 --> 00:34:47,670
to meet Su Yuanhang.

733
00:34:48,030 --> 00:34:48,630
We've now

734
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:49,710
caught him red-handed.

735
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,510
What's happening up front?

736
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:54,800
Gu Deyuan was the first to leave,

737
00:34:55,150 --> 00:34:56,630
with Gu Dezhao right on his heels.

738
00:34:57,320 --> 00:34:58,280
Good.

739
00:34:59,070 --> 00:35:01,190
Lest he be implicated

740
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:03,070
and drag the Ji family down with him.

741
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:08,440
He's finally learned some sense.

742
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,030
Did Gu Deyuan tip him off?

743
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:10,710
No,

744
00:35:11,110 --> 00:35:11,920
it was Miss Gu.

745
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:13,630
She deliberately

746
00:35:14,030 --> 00:35:15,230
undermined Lord Gu at the banquet.

747
00:35:15,590 --> 00:35:16,510
Every word he said,

748
00:35:16,710 --> 00:35:17,880
she shot him down,

749
00:35:18,230 --> 00:35:19,510
embarrassing him so badly

750
00:35:19,710 --> 00:35:20,710
in front of everyone

751
00:35:21,230 --> 00:35:21,960
that he had no choice but to leave.

752
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:24,880
Interesting.

753
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:28,440
She killed two birds with one stone.

754
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:31,030
Two birds with one stone?

755
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:32,480
She publicly

756
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:34,070
humiliated Gu Dezhao,

757
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:36,030
and kept him out of trouble.

758
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:38,230
What else would you call it?

759
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,480
But,

760
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:46,070
it harms her as much as it harms him.

761
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,230
Is everything ready outside?

762
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:49,070
All set.

763
00:35:51,510 --> 00:35:52,000
Good.

764
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,440
Let's go take a look.

765
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:54,360
Understood.

766
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:58,480
Master!

767
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:04,320
Bad news.

768
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:05,670
A lot of the guests are leaving.

769
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:07,360
Let them go.

770
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,150
Have you

771
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,510
