772
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,400
About what?

773
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:18,190
You fabricated this whole thing

774
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:20,190
to frame me!

775
00:36:20,630 --> 00:36:21,400
Frame you?

776
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:25,590
Has your steward

777
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:26,840
returned yet?

778
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,070
He went...

779
00:36:33,230 --> 00:36:34,590
Did you

780
00:36:35,030 --> 00:36:36,000
have him followed?

781
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:37,030
Thanks to him,

782
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,070
the Criminal Investigation Bureau

783
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:40,000
caught Su Yuanhang

784
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,590
without breaking a sweat.

785
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:42,840
Or rather,

786
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,590
thanks

787
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:46,960
to you.

788
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:01,030
Lord... Lord Chen,

789
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:03,360
please spare Su Yuanhang.

790
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:04,480
I will

791
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:07,230
submit my resignation at once,

792
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:09,590
I will yield the post

793
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:11,400
to... to...

794
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,510
Fu Hailian.

795
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:13,710
I'm afraid

796
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:16,150
