797
00:37:16,590 --> 00:37:18,320
Resignation needs a solid reason.

798
00:37:18,590 --> 00:37:19,550
What's more,

799
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:21,070
if His Majesty

800
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:22,280
