801
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:24,110
it will only cause more trouble.

802
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:31,150
What exactly do you want from me?

803
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:42,960
What...

804
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:45,000
You've amassed quite a fortune

805
00:37:45,150 --> 00:37:46,440
during your years in office.

806
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:48,320
Pleading guilty to corruption and

807
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:49,800
