808
00:37:50,230 --> 00:37:51,840
It's better than hiding undeclared land,

809
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:53,510
and a hundred times better than

810
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:54,880
secretly betraying and spying

811
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:56,590
on Grand Secretary Fan.

812
00:37:59,150 --> 00:38:00,110
Don't you agree?

813
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:09,110
Chen Yanyun,

814
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:11,960
you're slaving away for Fu Hailian.

815
00:38:12,150 --> 00:38:13,510
Have you ever thought about

816
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:15,320
what will happen to you in the end?

817
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:16,760
I haven't gotten around to that.

818
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,030
But

819
00:38:18,550 --> 00:38:20,710
thank you for the warning.

820
00:38:25,550 --> 00:38:26,320
Good day.

821
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:45,280
Miss!

822
00:38:46,150 --> 00:38:46,630
Miss!

823
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,510
Lin Xianzhong

824
00:38:48,510 --> 00:38:49,800
has been arrested.

825
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,070
What?

826
00:38:52,710 --> 00:38:54,150
I heard from the servants up front

827
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:55,070
that he was seized

828
00:38:55,070 --> 00:38:56,400
right at the banquet, on charges of

829
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:58,280
corruption and dereliction of duty.

830
00:38:58,590 --> 00:39:00,000
Everyone on Revenue Street

831
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:01,110
is talking about it right now.

832
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,440
It's Chen Yanyun.

833
00:39:07,510 --> 00:39:08,510
It has to be.

834
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:13,440
He moves

835
00:39:13,550 --> 00:39:14,590
so fast.

836
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:16,000
I entrusted

837
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,480
this critical mission

838
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:18,670
to your grandmother.

839
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:20,550
She must show her resolve,

840
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:21,880
prove she is willing

841
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:23,440
to burn her boats.

842
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:25,070
Only then

843
00:39:25,550 --> 00:39:27,710
can I fully trust her.

844
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:29,550
Do you

845
00:39:30,630 --> 00:39:31,760
agree?

846
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:36,000
Qingpu,

847
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,320
I think

848
00:39:38,710 --> 00:39:40,030
