849
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:42,710
Why?

850
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:45,590
I can't be sure yet.

851
00:39:46,630 --> 00:39:47,880
Something about this doesn't add up.

852
00:39:48,030 --> 00:39:48,510
Here,

853
00:39:48,510 --> 00:39:49,320
