856
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:01,800
[around the time of my ceremony.]

857
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,710
Sir, you're back.

858
00:40:17,070 --> 00:40:17,920
What are you doing here?

859
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:20,710
The letter Miss Gu

860
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:22,110
wrote to Old Madam Ji

861
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,230
was intercepted by our men

862
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,150
and brought here first.

863
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:26,510
Miss Gu?

864
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:39,400
Well?

865
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,150
Is there anything interesting in it?

866
00:40:42,150 --> 00:40:43,360
She writes that

867
00:40:44,070 --> 00:40:45,440
she met me once

868
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:46,400
while in the capital,

869
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:49,150
