886
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:14,840
For all her cleverness,

887
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:16,320
Miss Gu couldn't be that sharp.

888
00:41:16,630 --> 00:41:17,800
It might be because

889
00:41:18,110 --> 00:41:18,710
I deliberately rattled her

890
00:41:19,110 --> 00:41:20,440
at the Lin Manor that day.

891
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:22,590
Why?

892
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,070
